channel.title: Items become objects, rep+
channel.description:
Hi guys,
So i Made a webclient of MTP2 client from marcbob
but for a reason, My statius Warhammer, vesta longsword and chaotic maul become strange objects :|
i replaced the models in the cache like 100 times with 100 other models, but it doesn't seems to help
so if anyone know's a fix for this problem, Let me know!
[img]http://i42.servimg.com/u/f42/16/52/06/54/proble10.png[/img]

item.title: Items become objects, rep+
item.dc:creator: @Daginith Daginith
item.description:
@Daginith wrote:

[quote=“oldschool-scape, post:3, topic:433885”]Its the original client with the origional cache, i just made that it’s getting the cache out of the C://

the weird problem is its the same client and cache as my desktop client and if i use that one the items will show up, and if i use the webclient one that is reading the cache out of the C:// those 3 items become objects.[/quote]
it is possible there is another instance of the same cache name in your C:// drive, so the client felt no need to download the cache files, thus reading some old ones that don’t work well with your client. Try deleting the cache, then re-downloading i.
